## Print template (VX) widget

Print template (VX) widget can be used to display a template within another page or template.

To achieve that, drag and drop the widget to any page. In the widget options, you can search and select the name of the template you want to display.

For example, in the Stays demo dashboard, we use this widget to display the dashboard menu template in all the dashboard pages. This way, when we make changes to the dashboard menu, the changes are applied to all the dashboard pages at once
